msgstr "6 功能验证"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/MiniMax-M2.md:507
msgid ""
"Once your server is started, you can query the model with input prompts."
msgstr "服务器启动后，你可以使用输入提示查询模型。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/MiniMax-M2.md:509
msgid "**Note:**"
msgstr "**注意:**"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/MiniMax-M2.md:511
msgid ""
"`<node_ip>`: The IP address of the node where the server is running (e.g., "
"localhost for single-node)."
msgstr "`<node_ip>`: 运行服务器的节点IP地址（例如，单节点时为localhost）。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/MiniMax-M2.md:512
msgid ""
"`<port>`: The port number specified in the server startup command (e.g., "
"`8000`)."
msgstr "`<port>`: 服务器启动命令中指定的端口号（例如`8000`）。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/MiniMax-M2.md:514
msgid "Using curl"
msgstr "使用curl"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/MiniMax-M2.md:528
msgid ""
"Expected result: HTTP 200 with a JSON response containing a `choices` field "
"with the model's reply text."
msgstr "预期结果：HTTP 200，返回JSON响应，包含`choices`字段，其中包含模型的回复文本。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/MiniMax-M2.md:530
msgid "Using OpenAI Python Client"
msgstr "使用OpenAI Python客户端"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/MiniMax-M2.md:545
msgid ""
"Expected result: The response should contain a coherent self-introduction "
"and tool call parameter format in the `content` field."
msgstr "预期结果：响应应在`content`字段中包含连贯的自我介绍和工具调用参数格式。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/MiniMax-M2.md:547
msgid "Tool Calling Verification"
msgstr "工具调用验证"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/MiniMax-M2.md:576
msgid ""
